1/3 Finally fully recovered from COVID-19!
Fever completely stopped, difficulty breathing and cough are gone, and although my smell and taste is not fully back, I was able to finally have a hint of smell of these pretty roses.

Thank you for all your calls, texts & messages. https://t.co/d1LivyRgHb
